Titolo: Dragon Ball Z: Battle of Z

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Dragon Ball Z: Battle of Z is an action role-playing fighting game based on the Dragon Ball franchise. It was developed by Artdink and published by Bandai Namco Games. The game features elements from the 2013 Dragon Ball Z film, Battle of Gods, including the first appearance in a Dragon Ball video game of Goku's Super Saiyan God form, Beerus, and Whis.

